        "content_page": "<h4><strong>Official Rules</strong></h4><p><strong>NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND IS NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN THIS SWEEPSTAKES. A PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING. VOID WHERE PROHIBITED BY LAW.</strong></p><p><strong>ALL DISPUTES WILL BE RESOLVED SOLELY BY BINDING ARBITRATION AND ENTRANTS WAIVE THE ABILITY TO BRING CLAIMS IN A CLASS ACTION FORMAT.</strong></p><p>BY ENTERING (OR OTHERWISE PARTICIPATING IN) THE SWEEPSTAKES, ENTRANTS AGREE TO THESE OFFICIAL RULES, WHICH ARE A BINDING CONTRACT, SO READ THEM CAREFULLY BEFORE ENTERING.  WITHOUT LIMITATION, THIS CONTRACT INCLUDES INDEMNITIES TO THE SWEEPSTAKES ENTITIES FROM YOU AND A LIMITATION OF YOUR RIGHTS AND REMEDIES.</p><p><strong>1. Eligibility. </strong>For the Mamas Giveaway Sweepstakes (the \"Sweepstakes\") is open only to individuals who are legal residents and physically located in one (1) of the fifty (50) states in the United States or the District of Columbia who are at least eighteen (18) or older at the time of entry. Employees, officers and directors of Freestyle World, Inc. (\"Sponsor\"), and each of their respective affiliates, subsidiaries, advertising and promotion agencies, distributors and other prize suppliers (collectively with Sponsor, the \"Sweepstakes Entities\"), and each of such employees', officers' and directors' immediate family members and/or those living in the same household (whether legally related or not) of each are not eligible to enter the Sweepstakes or win a prize. For purposes of this Sweepstakes, immediate family members are defined as spouse, partner, parents, legal guardians, in-laws, grandparents, siblings, children and grandchildren and those living in the same household shall mean people who share the same residence at least three (3) months a year, whether legally related or not. Void where prohibited by law. (NEW JERSEY NOTICE: This Sweepstakes is not void in the state of New Jersey). By participating in the Sweepstakes, each entrant unconditionally accepts and agrees to comply with and abide by these \"Official Rules\" and the decisions of Sponsor, including the interpretation of these Official Rules and its exercise of discretion, which will be final and binding in all respects. The Sweepstakes is in no way sponsored, endorsed, approved, or administered by, or associated with, Instagram.</p><p><strong>2. Entry Period. </strong>The Sweepstakes begins on or about 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time (\"ET\") on June 15th, 2026 and all entries must be received by the Sponsor on or before 11:59 p.m. ET on June 22nd, 2026 (the \"Entry Period\").</p><p><strong>3. How to Enter. </strong>There are multiple ways to enter the Promotion:</p><p>During the Entry Period, Sponsor will collaborate on a post published on @6.lair's Instagram page regarding the Promotion (the \"Promotion Post\"). To enter:</p><ol><li>Follow: @freestyle.world, @6.lair, @yumi, and @pipettebaby</li><li>Like & Save the Promotion Post on Instagram</li><li>Tag one (1) friend in the comments of the Promotion Post. Each additional tag after the initial one (1) will add one (1) additional entry</li></ol><p>For 3 additional entries, please enter your email address on the landing page. By doing so you agree to receive marketing materials from Freestyle, Yumi and Pipette.</p><p><strong>Alternate Method of Entry (No Purchase Necessary): </strong>Alternate Method of Entry: During the Entry Period, email [freestyle.fam@freestyle.world](mailto: freestyle.fam@freestyle.world) address with your name and “entry to For the Mamas”. All entries must be received by the end of the Entry Period. Maximum of 10 entries regardless of entry method.\" Entries must be received by 11:59 p.m. ET on June 22nd, 2026.</p><p><strong>Maximum of 10 entries per person regardless of entry method.</strong></p><p>Sponsor may not receive entries that fail to strictly follow the posting instructions set forth in these Official Rules and Sponsor is not r